SUMMARY:The SATURDAY NIGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH! (Pubs\, Band\, DJ &
  Dancing)
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nHello everyone\,\n\n**Kindly Read 
 Carefully:**\n\nPlease join us for a unique **St. Paddy's** experience as 
 we hit\, not one but two great places to mix\, mingle and dance the night 
 away with Live Music\, Band\, DJ and awesome people!\n\nFirst we will meet
  at ***Duke of Kent (2nd Floor) You can ask the hostess at the front to di
 rect you to Steve's group upstairs)*** (Conveniently located extremely clo
 se Yonge & Eglinton corner. (2 minute walk north from the subway station)\
 n\nThe next venue is only minutes away from there (secret location)\n\n**W
 here to Meet us?**\n**Duke of Kent:** You will be directed upstairs to the
 re cool party room area :)\n**Date:** Saturday March 14th\, 2026\n**Addres
 s:** 2315 Yonge Street Toronto\, ON M4P 2X9\n**Arrive between:** 6:00 pm a
 nd 7:45 pm (if you can)\n(Encouraged earlier rather than later to have a c
 hance to meet everyone and soak up a great Saturday night)\n\n**Highlights
 :**\n\\*Reserved tables and seating for dinner\, cocktails and mingling\n\
 \*Venue is very close to the Yonge and Eglinton subway station\n\\*Ice bre
 aker game to make it easy to meet and connect with everyone :)\n\\*A fun g
 ame to win complimentary beverages :)\n\\*Live Music (Band) (DJ) and danci
 ng at our second secret location\n\n\\*Dress casual or dress up if you lik
 e :)\n**DRESS IN Green and have a Chance to win Sweets and Treats :)**\n\n
 -Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipate an awesome St
 . Paddy's Bash to remember!\n\n\\*One beverage or appetizer minimum at the
  first and second location-(No loitering please)\nThank you very much and 
 remember to Tip your Servers :)\n\\*a 3rd venue may be an option too depen
 ding on how everyone is feeling :)\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\nEvent Details be
 low:\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\nhttps://www.meetup.com/soulcity/
 \n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\nEvent Details:\n**The SATURDAY N
 IGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH!**\n**(Pubs\, Band\, DJ & Dancing)**\n\n-W
 e will meet ***upstairs in their party bar room area\;*** connect with eve
 ryone\, ice breaker game\, socialize\, share some laughs\, then make our w
 ay new our surprise location with live music\, DJ\, super fun atmosphere\,
  great people and dancing :)\n\\*Plan to come for dinner too if you like a
 t the first venue\, as tables will be reserved for everyone\n\n(All Venues
  will be close walking distance for us)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**EVENT FEE:**\n
 \n**Night of Event- Saturday March 14th (Arrival Times)**\n\n**\\*Ladies a
 nd Gents- Dress in Green if you can :)**\n-10 dollars if you arrive betwee
 n (6:00 pm and 7:30 pm)\n-15 dollars if you arrive between (7:31 pm and 8:
 50 pm)\n\nIf you arrive after that you will simply miss the event :)\n**(c
 ash or by e transfer to steveflemming11@gmail.com)**\n\n**DRESS IN GREEN a
 nd have a Chance to Win! :)**\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
